ABSTRACT

Retail organizations generate large volumes of sales data every day. Analyzing this data helps businesses understand customer purchasing behavior, optimize product placement, and improve sales performance.

This project uses Tableau to analyze retail sales data and create interactive dashboards. The dashboards visualize product performance, revenue trends, regional sales, customer demographics, and discount analysis. The insights generated help retailers make informed decisions to improve business efficiency and profitability.


