1. INTRODUCTION

Business Intelligence (BI) enables organizations to convert raw data into meaningful insights. Tableau is one of the leading BI tools used for creating interactive dashboards and visual reports.

The retail industry relies on data analysis to understand customer behavior, monitor sales trends, and improve inventory management. This project analyzes retail sales data to determine how product placement influences sales and revenue.


