Retail businesses often struggle to identify the best shelf placement, understand customer purchasing patterns, and analyze regional sales performance. Manual analysis is time-consuming and prone to errors.

This project solves these challenges by using Tableau dashboards to analyze retail sales data and generate meaningful business insights.


