7. BUSINESS INSIGHTS

Eye-level shelf placement generated the highest sales.

Dairy and Snacks contributed the highest revenue.

Moderate discounts increased sales volume.

The South region recorded the highest revenue.

Customers aged 25–40 made the majority of purchases.

Supermarkets performed better than convenience stores.



---

8. RECOMMENDATIONS

Place high-demand products at eye-level shelves.

Maintain sufficient stock for top-selling products.

Offer strategic discounts between 10% and 20%.

Focus marketing efforts on high-performing regions.

Review Tableau dashboards regularly for better decision-making.

Improve inventory planning using sales trends.



---

9. CONCLUSION

This project demonstrates how Tableau can transform retail sales data into meaningful business insights. By analyzing product placement, sales trends, customer demographics, and regional performance, retailers can make informed decisions that improve sales, optimize inventory, and enhance customer satisfaction.

The dashboards developed in this project provide an effective Business Intelligence solution for monitoring retail performance and supporting strategic planning.


